  "assessment_overview": {
    "intro": "Each criterion has eight possible achievement levels (1–8), divided into four bands representing performance that is: limited (1–2), adequate (3–4), substantial (5–6), and excellent (7–8). Each band has its own unique descriptor used to make best-fit judgments.",
    "requirement": "Subject groups must assess all strands of all four assessment criteria at least twice in each year of the MYP."
  },
